cu.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a string 'invalid' instead of a number will cause data type validation errors, leading to configuration parsing failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a string 'invalid' instead of a number will cause data type validation errors, leading to configuration parsing failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為字串 'invalid' 而非數字會導致資料型別驗證錯誤，造成配置解析失敗。
